                        <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Whether the switch is checked (two-way binding)</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm font-mono text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100">IsCheckedChanged</td>
                        <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">EventCallback&lt;bool&gt;</td>
                        <td class="px-6 py-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">-</td>
